{"tid":261587,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"成班人唔明咩係萬能DEGREE , 就亂吠","createTime":"2017-05-28T14:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T17:08:19.000Z","uid":108039,"like":7,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f933f49ffb7441ab7489e23d0220af635649d75","tid":261587,"uid":108039,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:50:15.000Z","msg":"班大電佬講人搶佢飯碗, 係咁水人地入CIVIL 同CS 。<br />\n我再重申一次: CS 呢個DEGREE 係八間院校都有, 而且係做唔過50歲, 詳見:香港IT人折墮實錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://hknoit.blogspot.hk/p/it.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhknoit.blogspot.hk%2Fp%2Fit.html&d=4Baf2qCrSLdHTNG60W%2FfEBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=77e88899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hknoit.blogspot.hk/p/it.html</a><br />\n<br />\n而且你真心唔係對某科特別有熱誠, 例如真係好鐘意PROGRAMMING 同ALGORITHMS 的話, 只係純粹為左日後有淡好食嘅話, CS 唔係一個選擇<br />\n第一, 任何一個ENGINE DEGREE 都可以DOUBLE MAJOR , 或MINOR CS<br />\n但係CS 畢業就做唔返佢地嘅野。<br />\n咁我地可以預測下年擁有CS RELATED 嘅人有幾多<br />\n(CIVIL + CS) + CS + (BSE+CS) +(EE +CS) + (ee +CS)  <br />\n第二, 既然可以咁樣玩, 點解要選擇一條最唔安全,即係純CS DEGREE 條路行, 因為你係做唔返相關工程嘅工作。 所以最安全嘅玩法, 係讀其他DEGREE 再MAJOR 或MINOR CS<br />\n第三, 既然選擇一項工程,當然選擇出路最多，而咁多出路最多一定係大電。<br />\n因為大電可以做電, 可以做BSE,又可以做IT, 又可以入BANK 做ANALYST <br />\n<br />\n所以大電叫做UNIVERSAL DEGREE"},{"pid":"ab8a28efb5e3c4de4b64702808130b10065d3959","tid":261587,"uid":108039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:52:35.000Z","msg":"第四, CIVIL 會爆"},{"pid":"67dfb37b9c34128a866e8476d7b3c0d7df8b6b40","tid":261587,"uid":108039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:58:20.000Z","msg":"班亂吠果班, 唔入來駁"},{"pid":"3573ee52e2e447ad14e0b2bf90b1edacbf5ff908","tid":261587,"uid":43717,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"大電佬一年都唔知有冇十個入到clients，想做BS又要再讀master。好似你講double major/minor就更加on9，邊讀得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />更何況你再take都唔夠cs,ce,ee嚟，一定唔請你<br />\n利申細電但入唔到IT工，乞緊食<br />\nce&gt;cs&gt;bs&gt;civil&gt;EE&gt;